		<div class="description-text">As we look to expand, JPP is seeking a well-organized, extremely self-motivated individual to help with the office management and day-to-day running of the office. The successful candidate will be someone who takes initiative, identifies problems and provides solutions and is able to work well under pressure. He or she will be able to multi-task and work with a team of investigators and lawyers to drive forward JPP's challenging, but rewarding, mission.</div>
		<div class="description-text mtop30">The role requires someone able to work full-time, 40-55 hours per week. Please note that while normal office hours are 9.30am - 5.00pm Monday - Friday, sometimes work outside of these hours - including the weekends - will be required.</div>
