			1.2 Work with the staff to develop and maintain office systems to increase the efficient functioning of the organization.<br>
			1.3 Open, stamp and deliver post daily.<br>
			1.4 Field and distribute email inquiries.<br>
			1.5 Manage the forward planning and diary of the founder and Director, Sarah Belal.<br>
			1.6 Take minutes of staff meetings.<br>
			1.7 Deal with stationery orders and assist staff with other operational tasks such as arrangement of couriers, travel, training and conference bookings.<br>
			1.8 Help to ensure a safe, pleasant, tidy and clutter-free office environment for JPP's staff and volunteers.<br>
			1.9 Create and maintain filing systems for the office of both casework and operational files.<br>
			1.10 Remain organized to ensure smooth management of the office.<br>
			1.11 Undertake other operational tasks as and when they arise.</div>

